Those blasted Red Fangs are pushing us too hard. I'm too pretty to fight, so I'm sending you.

Hunt down the {@LinkCreature:7#5#Red Fang orcans} and {@LinkCreature:7#6#fighters}.

Report to Kieran at Casidhe's Stand when your mission is complete.
Nicely done. If I survive this place, I'll simply stun the ladies with my good looks.
